"  2 tablespoons lower-sodium soy sauce","  2 tablespoons balsamic vinegar","  2 teaspoons Worcestershire sauce","  1/4 teaspoon salt","  1/4 teaspoon crushed red pepper","  1 tablespoon canola oil","  4 chicken drumsticks (about 1 pound), skinned","  4 chicken thighs (about 1 pound), skinned","  5 shallots, peeled (about 7 ounces)","  1/2 cup water","  1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","  2 large peeled sweet potatoes (about 1 pound), cut into 2-inch pieces","  1/2 cup raspberry spreadable fruit (such as Smucker's Simply Fruit)","  Thyme leaves (optional)"